def calculate_max_tokens(test_cases):
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        (N, capacities) = case
        ans = 1
        s = 0
        while len(capacities) > 0:
            d = min(capacities)
            ans += (d - s) * len(capacities)
            s = d
            capacities = capacities[:capacities.index(d)]
        results.append(ans)
    return results
